claim.claim-text:
A communication computer device for sharing media in a group communication among a plurality of wireless communications devices on a wireless communication network, the communication computer device configured to:
communicate with one or more of the plurality of wireless communications devices through the wireless communication network;
store information identifying the plurality of wireless communication devices as members of the group communication;
receive a group directed media file from a first wireless communication device identified as a first one of the members of the group communication for delivery to a second wireless communication device identified as a second one of the members of the group communication;
send the group directed media file to the second wireless communication device;
send the group directed media file to a data store;
communicate with the data store; and
selectively permit a third wireless communciations device identified as a third one of the members of the group communication to access the group-directed media file stored at the data store.

A method of sharing media in a group communication among a plurality of wireless communications devices on a wireless communication network comprising:
storing information identifying the plurality of wireless communication devices as members of the group communication;
receiving a group directed media file from a first wireless communication device identified as a first one of the members of the group communication for delivery to a second wireless communication device identified as a second one of the members of the group communication;
sending the group directed media file to the second wireless communication device;
sending the group directed media file to a data store;
communicating with the data store; and
selectively permitting a third wireless communciations device identified as a third one of the members of the group communication to access the group-directed media file stored at the data store.
